\c 18
\s Ukubotshwa kukaJesu
\p
\v 1 UJesu esekhulumile lezizinto waphuma kanye labafundi bakhe\x + Mat. 26.30.36. Mark. 14.26,32. Luka 22.39.\x* \add waya\add* ngaphetsheya kwesifudlana iKidroni\x + 2 Sam. 15.23.\x*, lapho okwakukhona isivande, angena kuso yena labafundi bakhe\x + Mat. 26.30.36. Mark. 14.26,32. Luka 22.39.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Njalo uJudasi laye, owamnikelayo, wayeyazi lindawo\x + Luka 22.40.\x*; ngoba uJesu wayebuthana khona labafundi bakhe kanengi\x + Luka 21.37. 22.39.\x*.
\v 3 Ngakho uJudasi, esethethe\x + Mat. 26.47-56. Mark. 14.43-50. Luka 22.47-53.\x* isigaba samabutho\x + 18.12. Mat. 27.27. Mark. 15.16. Seb. 10.1. 21.31. 27.1.\x*, labancedisi abavela kubapristi abakhulu labaFarisi\x + 18.12,18,22. Mat. 26.58.\x*, waya khona belezibane lamalambi lezikhali\x + Mat. 25.1. Isam. 4.5. 8.10. Seb. 20.8.\x*.
\v 4 Kwathi uJesu, ekwazi konke okwakuzamehlela, waphuma wathi kubo: Lidinga bani\x + 18.7. 1.38.\x*?
\v 5 Bamphendula \add bathi\add*: UJesu weNazaretha. UJesu wathi kubo: Mina ngingu\add ye\add*. LoJudasi owamnikelayo laye wayemi labo.
\v 6 Ngakho kuthe esithi kubo: Mina ngingu\add ye\add*; bahlehla nyovane, bawela phansi.
\v 7 Wasephinda wababuza \add wathi\add*: Lidinga bani? Basebesithi: UJesu weNazaretha.
\v 8 UJesu waphendula \add wathi\add*: Ngilitshelile ukuthi mina ngingu\add ye\add*; ngakho uba lidinga mina, yekelani laba bahambe;
\v 9 ukuze ligcwaliseke ilizwi ayelikhulumile elokuthi: Kulabo owanginika bona, angilahlekelwanga lamunye wabo\x + 17.12. 17.2.\x*.
\v 10 Kwathi uSimoni Petro elenkemba wayihwatsha, wagadla inceku yompristi omkhulu, waquma indlebe yayo yokunene. Lebizo lenceku lalinguMalikusi.
\v 11 UJesu wasesithi kuPetro: Faka inkemba yakho esikhwameni; inkezo uBaba anginike yona, kangiyikuyinatha yini\x + Mat. 20.22.\x*?
\p
\v 12 Ngakho isigaba\x + 18.12. Mat. 27.27. Mark. 15.16. Seb. 10.1. 21.31. 27.1.\x*\x + Seb. 21.31.\x* samabutho lenduna\x + Seb. 21.31.\x* labancedisi bamaJuda bambamba uJesu\x + 18.12,18,22. Mat. 26.58.\x*, bambopha,
\v 13 basebemusa\x + Mat. 26.57.\x* kuqala kuAnasi\x + 18.24. Luka 3.2. Seb. 4.6.\x*; ngoba wayenguyisezala kaKayafasi\x + Mat. 26.3.\x*, owayengumpristi omkhulu ngalowomnyaka\x + 11.49,51.\x*.
\v 14 Kwakunguye uKayafasi owayecebise amaJuda, ukuthi kwakulungile ukuthi umuntu oyedwa afele isizwe\x + 11.50. 19.11.\x*.
\s UPetro ulandula uJesu. Ukuthethwa kwecala likaJesu
\p
\v 15 USimoni Petro wasemlandela uJesu\x + Mat. 26.58. Mark. 14.54. Luka 22.54.\x*, lomunye umfundi. Lalowomfundi wayesaziwa ngumpristi omkhulu, wangena loJesu egumeni lompristi omkhulu\x + Mat. 26.3.\x*;
\v 16 kodwa uPetro wayemi ngaphandle emnyango\x + 18.16,17. Mat. 26.69,70. Mark. 14.66-68. Luka 22.55-57.\x*. Wasephuma lowomfundi omunye owayesaziwa ngumpristi omkhulu, wasekhuluma lomlindisangokazi, wamngenisa uPetro\x + Seb. 12.13.\x*.
\v 17 Incekukazi encane engumlindisango yasisithi kuPetro: Kawusuye lawe omunye wabafundi balumuntu yini? Yena wathi: Kangisu\add ye\x + Mark. 14.66.\x*\add*.
\v 18 Njalo izinceku labancedisi\x + 18.12,18,22. Mat. 26.58.\x* babemi bebase umlilo wamalahle, ngoba kwakumakhaza\x + 21.9.\x*, njalo besotha; uPetro laye wayemi labo esotha.
\p
\v 19 Umpristi omkhulu wasembuza uJesu ngabafundi bakhe, langemfundiso yakhe\x + Mat. 26.59-68. Mark. 14.55-65. Luka 22.63-71.\x*.
\v 20 UJesu wamphendula \add wathi\add*: Mina ngikhulume obala emhlabeni\x + 16.25.\x*; ngezikhathi zonke mina bengifundisa esinagogeni\x + Luka 4.15. Joha. 6.59.\x* lethempelini\x + Mat. 26.55.\x*, lapho amaJuda abuthana khona ngesikhathi sonke, njalo kangikhulumanga lutho ensitha\x + Isa. 45.19. 48.16.\x*.
\v 21 Ubuzelani kimi? Buza labo abakuzwayo lokho engakukhuluma labo\x + 5.31.\x*; khangela, bona bayazazi izinto mina engazitshoyo\x + 7.46.\x*.
\v 22 Kwathi esetshilo lezizinto, omunye wabancedisi\x + 18.3,12,18.\x* owayemi khona wamwakala\f + \fk wamwakala: \fl kumbe, \fq wamtshaya ngenduku.\f* uJesu\x + 19.3. Mat. 26.67. 1 Kho. 22.24.\x*, esithi: Kanti uphendula njalo umpristi omkhulu\x + Seb. 23.4.\x*?
\v 23 UJesu wamphendula \add wathi\add*: Uba ngikhulume kubi, fakaza ngobubi; kodwa uba kuhle, ungitshayelani?
\v 24 UAnasi wasemthuma ebotshiwe kuKayafasi umpristi omkhulu\x + Mat. 26.57. Joha. 18.13.\x*.
\p
\v 25 Kodwa uSimoni Petro wayemi esotha\x + 18.18.\x*; basebesithi kuye: Kawusuye lawe \add omunye\add* wabafundi bakhe yini? Waphika yena, wathi: Kangisu\add ye\x + Mat. 26.71-75. Mark. 14.69-72. Luka 22.58-62.\x*\add*.
\v 26 Omunye wezinceku zompristi omkhulu, oyisinini somuntu uPetro aquma indlebe yakhe\x + 18.10.\x*, \add wathi\add*: Mina kangikubonanga yini esivandeni ulaye?
\v 27 UPetro wasebuya ephika; njalo lahle lakhala iqhude\x + 13.38.\x*.
\s UJesu uphambi kukaPilatu
\p
\v 28 Basebemkhupha uJesu\x + Mat. 27.2. Mark. 15.1. Luka 23.1.\x* kuKayafasi bamusa endlini yombusi\x + 18.24. Luka 22.66-71.\x*; njalo kwakusekuseni, kodwa kabangenanga bona endlini yombusi, ukuze bangangcoli\x + Seb. 10.28. 11.3.\x*, kodwa ukuze badle iphasika\x + 19.14.\x*.
\p
\v 29 Ngakho uPilatu waphumela kubo, wathi: Limbeka cala bani lumuntu\x + Mat. 27.11-14. Mark. 15.2-5. Luka 23.2,3.\x*?
\v 30 Basebephendula bathi kuye: Uba lo ubengesuye owenza okubi\x + 1 Pet. 2.12.\x*, ngabe kasimnikelanga kuwe.
\v 31 UPilatu wasesithi kubo: Mthatheni lina, limahlulele njengomlayo wakini\x + Seb. 24.6.\x*. Ngakho amaJuda athi kuye: Kakuvunyelwa kithi ukubulala umuntu;
\v 32 ukuze kugcwaliseke ilizwi uJesu alikhulumayo, ukutshengisa uhlobo lokufa ayezakufa ngalo\x + Mat. 20.19. Mark. 10.33. Luka 18.32. Joha. 12.32,33.\x*.
\p
\v 33 Ngakho uPilatu wabuye wangena endlini yombusi, wambiza uJesu, wathi kuye: Wena uyiNkosi yamaJuda yini\x + Luka 23.2.\x*?
\v 34 UJesu wamphendula \add wathi\add*: Uyazitsholo lokhu wena yini, kumbe abanye bakutshelile ngami?
\v 35 UPilatu waphendula \add wathi\add*: Kanti ngingumJuda mina? Isizwe sakini labapristi abakhulu bakunikele kimi; wenzeni?
\v 36 UJesu waphendula \add wathi\add*: Umbuso wami\x + Dan. 2.44. 7.14,27. Joha. 6.15.\x* kawusiwo walumhlaba\x + 8.23.\x*; uba umbuso wami ubungowalumhlaba\x + 8.23.\x*, inceku zami\x + Mat. 26.53.\x* bezizakulwa\x + Luka 13.24.\x*, ukuze nginganikelwa kumaJuda\x + 19.16.\x*; kodwa khathesi umbuso wami kawusiwo owalapha.
\v 37 UPilatu wasesithi kuye: Ngakho uyinkosi yini? UJesu waphendula \add wathi\add*: Uyatsho wena, ukuthi mina ngiyinkosi\x + Mat. 27.11.\x*. Mina ngazalelwa lokhu, njalo ngizele lokhu emhlabeni\x + 12.27.\x*, ukuze ngifakazele\x + 1 Tim. 6.13.\x* iqiniso\x + 17.17,19.\x*. Wonke oweqiniso uyalizwa ilizwi lami\x + 8.47. 1 Joha. 3.18,19. 4.6.\x*.
\v 38 UPilatu wathi kuye: Liyini iqiniso?
\p Kwathi esetshilo lokhu, wabuya waphumela kumaJuda\x + 19.4.18.33.\x*, wathi kuwo: Mina kangitholi lacala kuye\x + Mat. 27.24. Mark. 15.14. Luka 23.4. Joha. 19.4,6. Seb. 3.13.\x*.
\v 39 Kodwa lilomkhuba, wokuthi ngilikhululele omunye ngephasika; ngakho liyathanda ukuthi ngilikhululele iNkosi yamaJuda yini\x + 18.39,40. Mat. 27.15-26. Mark. 15.6-15. Luka 23.17-25.\x*?
\v 40 Wonke asememeza futhi\x + 18.30. Mark. 15.13.\x*, athi: Hatshi lo, kodwa uBarabasi\x + Seb. 3.14.\x*; kodwa uBarabasi wayengumphangi\x + Mat. 26.55. Mark. 15.7. Luka 23.19.\x*.